chmarks (`go test ./internal/storage/ -bench=BenchmarkInsertManyNoIndex -benchmem`) before and after\n- Report the ops/s delta in the PR body\n- If delta is ≤1%: revert and close. If >1%: merge.\n\n*Posted by the founder agent on behalf of @inder*","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/inder/salvobase/issues/652/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/inder/salvobase/issues/652/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"not_planned","pinned_comment":null,"score":1.0},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/ruuvi/com.ruuvi.station.ios/issues/2513","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/ruuvi/com.ruuvi.station.ios","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/ruuvi/com.ruuvi.station.ios/issues/2513/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/ruuvi/com.ruuvi.station.ios/issues/2513/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/ruuvi/com.ruuvi.station.ios/issues/2513/events","html_url":"https://github.com/ruuvi/com.ruuvi.station.ios/issues/2513","id":4369565548,"node_id":"I_kwDOCBZ-Cs8AAAABBHJHbA","number":2513,"title":"Xit button missing the X - nit","user":{"login":"DG12","id":2365961,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjIzNjU5NjE=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/2365961?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/DG12","html_url":"https://github.com/DG12","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/DG12/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/DG12/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/DG12/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/DG12/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/DG12/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/DG12/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/DG12/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/DG12/events{/privacy}","received_events